    • hasAttribute

      public static org.hamcrest.Matcher<org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext> hasAttribute​(String attribute, String value)
      Creates an instance of HasAttributeMatcher that checks some attribute of an instance of SearchContext. It should be WebElement or some implementor of HasAttribute. Otherwise the matching returns false. It is expected that value of the attribute is equal to the defined value.
      Parameters:
      attribute - to be checked
      value - is expected to be equal to value of the attribute.
      Returns:
      instance of HasAttributeMatcher

    • hasAttribute

      public static org.hamcrest.Matcher<org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext> hasAttribute​(String attribute)
      Creates an instance of HasAttributeMatcher that checks some attribute of an instance of SearchContext. It should be WebElement or some implementor of HasAttribute. Otherwise the matching returns false. It is expected that value of the attribute is not null or empty value.
